original: Leffler, Sven Arne Alfred Gustaf, tandläkare, Skara, f. 4/8/06 i Södertälje av rektor Gustaf L. o. Svea Egge. G. 35 m. tandl. Dagny Niklasson. Barn: Sven f. 36, Kerstin 38, Cecilia 46. — Stud:ex. i Skara 27, Cand. med. dent. i Greifswald 29, tysk tandläk. där 31, sv. tandläk. 33. Praktik i Grebbestad 33-36, i Skara sed. 36.
translated: Leffler, Sven Arne Alfred Gustaf, dentist, Skara, b. 4/8/06 in Södertälje to principal Gustaf L. and Svea Egge. Married in 1935 to dentist Dagny Niklasson. Children: Sven b. 1936, Kerstin b. 1938, Cecilia b. 1946. — High school graduate in Skara in 1927, dental degree from Greifswald in 1929, practicing as a German dentist there in 1931, Swedish dentist in 1933. Practice in Grebbestad from 1933-1936, in Skara since 1936.

education.description: Practiced as a German dentist in Greifswald
Practiced as a Swedish dentist in Skara
